  ('medical-tech-moex-00297', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-112-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種檢測急性C型肝炎病毒感染的方法最不適當？', '["C型肝炎病毒抗原檢驗（HCV antigen test）", "C型肝炎病毒RNA定性檢驗（HCV RNA qualitative test）", "C型肝炎病毒RNA定量檢驗（HCV RNA quantitative test）", "C型肝炎病毒分離（HCV isolation）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:29+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6ded8338776e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "de093d821ec4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112020", "c": "308", "s": "66", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
